dc_description_s: This data represents bear hunting management zones for Wisconsin in 2021. [This is a polygon feature class representing Wisconsin DNR Bear Management Zones. Bear Management Zones indicate the areas with various bear hunting regulations throughout Wisconsin. Hunting regulations may vary between and within zones. Users should consult the most recent Hunting Regulations Handbook to determine which regulations apply to which zones, or portions of zones. Bear Management Zones allow the DNR to better control the distribution of hunters and shift hunting pressure to areas of high nuisance and/or damage complaints.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-wi-dnr.opendata.arcgis.com/datasets/bear-hunting-management-zones?geometry=-101.700%2C42.002%2C-77.705%2C47.459
